&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://wargaming.com/media/ckeditor_uploads/2025/08/26/Banner-SM-648%20x%20211-Version300ppi.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;648&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wargaming is looking for a Balance Designer to work on a World of Tanks Console game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Create collision models for new vehicles and edit collision models of existing vehicles;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Set up armor values of vehicles in an internal editor and xml files;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Communicate with 3D modelers, historical consultants, balance designers.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;English - B1 and higher;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Very experienced World of Tanks player, excellent knowledge of game mechanics;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Technical mindset and ability to think in 3D.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What additional skills will help you stand out?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Experience working with 3D editors (Maya, 3D Max, Blender, etc.);&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Familiarity with game engines (Unreal, Unity, etc.).&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hybrid (2-3 days of work from the office)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role isn&#39;t eligible for relocation &amp;amp; immigration support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits and perks are tailored to the local market and culture. Our benefits in Belgrade include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Additional vacation days based on years of service at Wargaming: up to 5 days on top of the statutory minimum&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional paid time off (5 Personal Days, Birthday Leave, Marriage Leave, Compassionate Leave)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sick Leave Compensation, Maternity Leave Benefits &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Premium Private Health Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Career development and education opportunities within the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English clubs and platform for learning languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mental well-being program (iFeel)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commuting allowance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FitPass membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discounts for employees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal Gaming Account&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coffee, fruits, and snacks in the office&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On-site canteen with subsidized prices for food and drinks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seniority Awards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Referral program - you can recommend the best talents to the Company and receive a reward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Please submit your CV in English to ensure smooth processing and review.&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;About Wargaming&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wargaming is an award-winni

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://wargaming.com/media/ckeditor_uploads/2025/08/26/Banner-SM-648%20x%20211-Version300ppi.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;648&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Job Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role&amp;nbsp;is responsible for&amp;nbsp;owning and&amp;nbsp;representing&amp;nbsp;the English-speaking World of Tanks community at a professional level. You will act as a key bridge between players and the product, combining strong game knowledge, analytical capability, and clear communication to support both community health and business decisions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The role requires someone who can confidently engage with players, interpret sentiment, and communicate effectively across a range of situations, from day-to-day interactions to high-visibility and live-audience settings. Therefore&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;, the role is best suited for someone with prior experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You will work closely with publishing, social media, competitive gaming, and livestream teams to deliver a cohesive global strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Reports to&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Senior Community Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What will you do?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Own and actively manage the English-speaking World of Tanks community across official platforms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Act as a credible voice of the product, demonstrating strong in-game knowledge, including mechanics, meta, systems, and player&amp;nbsp;behavior.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Translate community sentiment into clear, structured reports with actionable insights for internal stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Communicate effectively in high-visibility and complex situations, including interactions with content creators and community leaders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Represent the product in live and high-visibility formats, including livestreams, presentations, or community events, with clear and confident communication.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Drive engagement through discussions, initiatives, and community-led activities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Identify and support key community contributors and creators.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Monitor,&amp;nbsp;analyze, and report on community KPIs and sentiment trends.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally to ensure consistent messaging and execution of publishing plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Proactively support a constructive and engaged community environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What are we looking for?&

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://wargaming.com/media/ckeditor_uploads/2025/08/26/Banner-SM-648%20x%20211-Version300ppi.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;648&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Full Stack Developer to join the World of Tanks Console team, with a strong focus on backend systems and live-service platform integration. While the role is titled &quot;Full Stack,&quot; the day-to-day work is heavily weighted toward backend engineering - building and maintaining the services that support core gameplay systems, player data, and platform integrations across a live, high-traffic console title.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports to&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Solution Architect&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and maintain backend services supporting live-service functionality for World of Tanks Console&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and integrate platform-specific authentication and services (Xbox, PlayStation Network, Steam)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement REST APIs used across internal and platform-facing systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with distributed messaging systems to support scalable, event-driven architecture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure reliability and performance of production systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to infrastructure and deployment practices using containerized and orchestrated environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in Python, including async Python (asyncio)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with PostgreSQL and MySQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with RabbitMQ / AMQP messaging systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Redis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Docker and Kubernetes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of REST API design principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
