&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience as a Game Designer of products with successful releases ;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing progression, matchmaking, or social systems;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Game design experience on live service/games-as-a-service titles in the midcore/hardcore action game sphere;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A progressive critical thinker who can develop solutions to overcome the obstacles and challenges that come with new game development.&lt;/li&gt;
