&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wargaming&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;is looking for a talented &lt;strong&gt;UI Developer&lt;/strong&gt; to join the World of Tanks Modern Armor team in &lt;strong&gt;Belgrade&lt;/strong&gt;. You&#39;ll build high-quality UI systems, transform UX designs into seamless in-game experiences, and develop scalable frontend solutions that delight millions of players around the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports to&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Development Director&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translates UI/UX designs and wireframes into high-quality frontend systems that match intended user experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies, analyses and resolves issues in UI systems, including rendering artifacts, input handling problems, cross-platform incompatibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborates with UX designers and engineers from game and engine teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Owns UI component libraries, UI systems and frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluates requirements and designs for alignment with performance targets, technical feasibility and integration with owned systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Owns systems in production, ensuring reliability, performance, and maintainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writes clean, efficient code that follows project coding standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designs, builds, and maintains systems and services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimizes systems for performance, scalability, and stability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participates in code reviews and collaborates on technical decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Documents architectures, APIs, and systems so they can be understood, extended, and maintained&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in UI development, Web Frontend in game development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Programming skills in any of the scripting languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermediate English - B2 or higher&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What additional skills will help you stand out?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own game projects with UI development part&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with OOP languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AS3 development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Adobe Animate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Python or LUA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hybrid (3 days of work from the office)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role isn&#39;t eligible for relocation &amp;amp; immigration support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
